item.title: Welcome to Preskinole!
item.description: We are the premier Prescott, AZ crokinole club. Founded in 2024 we are more than 3 members strong and have events nearly every other month.

item.title: Membership
item.description: Welcome new member! We don’t really do or offer anything, so if you want to be a member, you already are!
